  "description": "A massive Maersk Antares container ship is being guided into port by a tugboat on a sunny day. The ship is brightly colored with stacked shipping containers in shades of red, blue, green, and yellow. The tugboat, a white and yellow vessel, is positioned in front of the ship, appearing to assist in maneuvering. In the background, a port facility with a crane is visible, along with other ships and a blue sky. The water is a dark blue and is rippled by the movement of the vessels. The scene evokes a sense of global trade and maritime activity.",
